ii. 267: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilaAlN","text_ar":"طِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilalN","text_ar":"طِلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) the latter mentioned by Fr, and said by him to be the only instance of the kind that has been heard except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HirafN","text_ar":"حِرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarofN","text_ar":"حَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harof","text_ar":"حَرْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a mountain; (O;) [or]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalalN","text_ar":"طَلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TilaAlN","text_ar":"طِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in a saying of a poet, cited by IAar, (TA,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~alal","text_ar":"الطَّلَل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~al~","text_ar":"الطَّلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ul~","text_ar":"الطُّلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or in this instance, as some relate it, the word is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ilal","text_ar":"الطِّلَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA biAln~aAqapi","text_ar":"مَا بِالنَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in the she-camel any milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"], as Yaakoob says, and as is related on the authority of AA, (S,) and thus in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA biAld~aAri Tul~N","text_ar":"مَا بِالدَّارِ طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in the house any milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies thus: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blood."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [But see this word below.]) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paucity of milk of a camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiroqN","text_ar":"طِرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in my MS. copy of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuroqN","text_ar":"طُرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: thus in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA biAln~aAqapi Tal~N","text_ar":"مَا بِالنَّاقَةِ طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in the she-camel any fat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K, TA: in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  [It is also used as an epithet.] You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN Tal~N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw Tal~K","text_ar":"ذُو طَلٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A day having drizzling rain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dew;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"humid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN Tal~apN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land moistened by dew"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by drizzling rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maToluwlapN","text_ar":"مَطْلُولَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and [in like manner]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~apN","text_ar":"طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a meadow ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoDapN","text_ar":"رَوْضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moistened by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~","text_ar":"طَلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~N","text_ar":"طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies Anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moist."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus applied to a night, and to poetry ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEor","text_ar":"شِعْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEar","text_ar":"شَعَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]), and to water, &c.: (K, TA:) applied to these as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so to discourse; (TA;) and thus ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaliylapN","text_ar":"طَلِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobap","text_ar":"خُطْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN Tal~apN","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A beautiful, elegant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"graceful, woman."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamorN Tal~apN","text_ar":"خَمْرٌ طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pleasant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicious, wine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K: *) or, as"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1863},{"kind":"text","text":"some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as descends easily"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasantly down the throat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~apN","text_ar":"طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to an odour ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHapN","text_ar":"رَايِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, TA, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ray~aA","text_ar":"رَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) likewise signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pleasant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)       -A3-  Also An"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aged"},{"kind":"text","text":"man: (Kr, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~apN","text_ar":"طَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies an"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old"},{"kind":"text","text":"woman: (K, TA:) and a woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul, unseemly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene, in tongue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"annoying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"molesting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A serpent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) thus accord. to IAar: (O:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Til~N","text_ar":"طِلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) thus accord. to AA; (O;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiloEN","text_ar":"طِلْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","O","TA","Kr"]},{"entry_id":"n26869","headword_ar":"طُلٌّ","root":"Tl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~N","text_ar":"طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. [But the signification of “ blood ” there mentioned requires consideration; for Sgh adds immediately after explaining the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA biAld~aAri Tul~N","text_ar":"مَا بِالدَّارِ طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"what here follows.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba damuhu Tul~FA","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ دَمُهُ طُلًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Til~FA","text_ar":"طِلًّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadarFA","text_ar":"هَدَرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His blood went for nought, unretaliated, and uncompensated by a mulct"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ibn-'Abbád, O. [Then follows immediately in the O"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ul~aA='u","text_ar":"الطُّلَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. as below.])"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26870","headword_ar":"طِلٌّ","root":"Tl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~N","text_ar":"طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tul~N","text_ar":"طُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}